- The average rating is calculated by dividing the sum of all ratings by the number of reviews;
- Customer reviews are considered more important in the context of verifying the quality of a coffee shop;
- Owner reviews might include promotional content and are sometimes less reliable.

- "average rating above 4" refers to coffee shops that have received a rating of 4 or higher out of 5;
- "wireless connection to the digital world" refers to Wi-Fi availability;
- "a power outlet for your devices" refers to the presence of sockets;
- "accessibility for all" refers to wheelchair accessibility.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(coffee_shop_id) AS total_verified_coffee_shops
FROM coffee_shops
WHERE verified = 1 AND last_updated IS NOT NULL AND last_updated != '';

